This is my friend Christine, who I had the pleasure of meeting this past spring when she shared her lung cancer journey with our Tackle Radon team. Christine was diagnosed with radon-induced lung cancer in her thirties. Radon is the second leading cause of lung cancer and if your home has high levels, you could be at risk. Together, Christine and I encourage you to test your home for radon and protect your family. Please test today at TackleRadon.ca
 
#TackleRadon #LungCancer #radon

Everyday Dose is a mushroom infused coffee along with L-Theanine and Collagen. I have to say I’m loving adding this to my morning routine. It’s with a very heavy heart that I write this post. My dad, Andrew Bighill passed away last week on June 27th. It was not expected and quite sudden, and it still doesn’t feel real to me. There’s so much I could say here, and none of it would completely do it justice to completely honor my dad. I’ll say this, he was the most unselfish and loving person I have known, and dedicated his entire life to me. Thank you Dad, I love you so much.

We will be holding a memorial service on a July 22nd in Long Beach Washington at Pentilla’s Chapel By The Sea at 11am. A potluck reception, either bringing food or a memorial donation, will be held after at another location near by. For those looking at attending, please reach out @kristinabighill to confirm your attendance as we would love to celebrate Andy’s life with all of those who knew him.

social_posts.post_text:
Was nice to get away to @staylakehouse for a couple days and recharge. We stayed in the Marigold Cottage and you can see from this reel how amazing the space was. 

Not only we did we experience some great hikes and outdoors with the great weather, but we had an amazing show from the northern lights at night. 

The restaurant at @staylakehouse has some of the best and most delicious food creations I’ve came across. You know it’s good when you could see yourself ordering everything on the menu.

If you haven’t been up to Clear Lake, I definitely recommend it! Until next time ✌🏼

#staylakehouse #marigoldcottage #exploremb #discoverclearlake #manitobafood #manitobafoodie
